    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolutely wonderful to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes and weekend trips. Everything runs smoothly, and the interior is still looking great! If you're looking for a dependable car that's been well-loved and taken care of, this is definitely the one for you. I've truly enjoyed driving it, and I'm sure you will too. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great new home!",
      "price": 34500.0,
