    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and serves as a reliable, stylish daily driver. The exterior retains a deep gloss with only minor, age-appropriate road wear, while the interior remains exceptionally clean, smoke-free, and features fully functional electronics throughout. Mechanically, it is in great health, backed by a comprehensive service history and recent fluid changes. It drives smoothly, shifts precisely, and offers the peace of mind that comes from a well-loved car. It is the perfect choice for a buyer seeking a high-quality, turn-key vehicle without the showroom price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
